      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 You have seriously got to see this absolute beauty. It is in truly pristine condition\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one and it really shows! It drives like an absolute dream and looks just as gorgeous as the day it rolled off the lot. If you're looking for something that feels brand new but without that brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I'm happy to answer any questions you have, so feel free to reach out and let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 44900.0,
