    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering an investment-grade E46 M3 in concours condition. This specimen features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, boasting individual throttle bodies and a recently recalibrated double VANOS system for optimal cam phasing. The drivetrain is anchored by a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory-spec limited-slip differential. Mechanically, this vehicle is superlative: the rear subframe has been reinforced as a preventative measure, and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells for long-term reliability. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with fresh bushings and original dampers. A true turn-key example for the discerning collector seeking peak atmospheric performance.",
